{"id":"sarai","term":"Sarai","source":"Easton's Bible Dictionary (M.G. Easton, 1897)","html":"<p>My princess, the name originally borne by Sarah (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Genesis 11:31\">Gen. 11:31</a>; <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Genesis 17:15\">17:15</a>).</p>\n\u0000","refs":["Genesis 11:31","Genesis 17:15"]}